## 2. 実行後の確認 (dpkg)
$ ssh oci-portfolio "dpkg -l | grep -E 'iptables|persistent|ufw'"
ii  iptables                               1.8.10-3ubuntu2                                  arm64        administration tools for packet filtering and NAT
ii  python3-pyrsistent:arm64               0.20.0-1build2                                   arm64        persistent/functional/immutable data structures for Python
